snippet.title: Wendy Williams Furiously Reacts To Battling Dementia After Losing Her Show
snippet.description:
Wendy Williams Furiously Reacts To Battling Dementia After Losing Her Show 
Popular talk show host of The Wendy Williams Show, Wendy Williams has had a rough couple of months, hell years, health-wise.
The TV personality has faced so many blocks of health hurdles and it hasn’t been easy for her to cross them. Wendy, widely known and popular for her brutal honesty and harsh criticism of A-list celebrities she often interviews, has faced over a decade of different health and personal struggles. 
The TV star hasn’t always been a TV star. She started off as radio DJ and host for which she was known as the ‘New York’s Shock Jockette’.
